需返回寫字樓辦公，而是留在家中工作。<br />\n<br />\n  有關安排暫定實行至二月二日，政府屆時會再檢視情況。<br />\n<br />\n  政府發言人呼籲私人機構在可行情況下，作類似安排。<br />\n<br />\n  個別政府部門會就受影響的公共服務作出公布。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年1月28日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間11時20分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:23:51.000Z","msg":"醫護、入境、海關、衞生署成為condom<br />\n高官及文職同你地割蔗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pd0xhvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPd0xhvm.jpg&h=e650018e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"deb12e0c13b191f1f8b65b684f23d2e561d2454b","tid":1847223,"uid":136147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:24:06.000Z","msg":"所有醫護即刻home office 學李克強咁係屋企著防護服就叫扮工"},{"pid":"a1408a59f026511dcf7511870934dfaa1bcbbd1a","tid":1847223,"uid":186814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"又唔驚引起恐慌 同埋 顧及市民同遊客感受喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf014e269118be3c85742b72f281fe6f4b1a9f6e","tid":1847223,"uid":27395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1682754408db842c64c6f471bff791e2a9c5ef10","tid":1847223,"uid":240448,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"政府僱員就係唔同d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通打工仔就........."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"班前線都做左condom啦"},{"pid":"a818a66acd27b67e280cac30f2a6b2426560ed13","tid":1847223,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf014e269118be3c85742b72f281fe6f4b1a9f6e","tid":1847223,"uid":27395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1682754408db842c64c6f471bff791e2a9c5ef10","tid":1847223,"uid":240448,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"政府僱員就係唔同d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smi